  "texts": [
    "In the absence of an existing account, the system creates one for the employee, and a clerk reviews the amount, reformulating it if necessary before submission to the manager.",
    "If the amount falls below a specified threshold, it is promptly approved; otherwise, if it exceeds this threshold, the manager evaluates it.",
    "In case of rejection, the process terminates immediately.",
    "However, if approved, the corresponding amount is transferred to the applicant's bank account, accompanied by an approval notification, thus successfully concluding the process.",
    "Experimental settingThe proposed BPLLM system is based on generative models and hence it generates feedback for the user in natural language."
  ],
